      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This impeccably maintained vehicle represents the perfect balance of performance and long-term value. Having undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection, it stands as a testament to responsible ownership, offering a driving experience that is as smooth as it is dependable. With its clean interior and robust mechanical profile, this car is ready to provide years of reliable service to its next discerning owner. Experience the confidence of a premium pre-owned vehicle that doesn't compromise on quality or style.",
